<br>
-No level or class or race restrictions<br>
    (not everyone is into every aspect of the game)<br>
-you DO require a DC member in good standing to sponsor you.<br>
    (By vouching for a potential member a DC member must already trust you, and believe you are good for the guild. By giving their sponsorship they are showing that they believe in you.)<br>
-Honor is required for membership<br>
    (All wearing the DC tag should be able to trust each other and be trusted by others even outside the guild implicitely and completely. If a member cannot be trusted they do not belong in DC)<br>
-Wear the tag with pride<br>
    (DC is NOT a stepping stone. It is the hope of all of DC that any members would treat it as a marriage and would help in its evolution as we grow.)<br>
__<br>
Basically DC is all about Honor and Fun. :-)<br>
